Package net.sourceforge.JDash.ecu.param

Interface Summary
DoubleParameter Most parameters are of type Double.
ParameterEventListener  
StringParameter This interface is used by the JDAsh system to identify parameters that are string values, and NOT double values.
 

Class Summary
DTCMetaParam DTCs are a different thing all together.
ECUParameter An ECU Parameter is an extension to the minimum parameter.
JSMetaParam This meta param will take a single parameter named "script" and run the script against the values using BeanShell.
MetaParameter A MetaParameter is an abstract class that represents a parameter value that is somewhat dynamic.
Parameter This basic parameter class is simple class whos sole purpose is to provide data to the renderers/Observers.
ParameterComparator The parameter comparator.
ParameterRegistry  
XMLParameterLoader This class will read an XML based parameter file to create parameters as needed.
